## 4. Commenting requirements

### 4.1 Comment all non-obvious logic
You must add comments for:
- recommendation and ranking logic
- threshold selection logic
- benchmark handle mapping logic
- builder handoff logic
- caching logic
- fallbacks and error handling
- any dependency on Shopify-specific constraints

### 4.2 Do not add useless comments
Bad comment:
- `// set variable`

Good comment:
- `// Map benchmark handles to the cheapest in-stock sellable product so FPS results stay tied to actual store inventory.`

### 4.3 Comment structure
Prefer comments that explain:
- why this exists
- what assumption it depends on
- what could break if changed

